The paper deals with error-control codes for RAM chips, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The use of RAM chips is also related to data structures (cs.DS) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions the weight distribution of codes, which is a topic in coding theory and error-correcting codes (cs.EM). Finally, the paper deals with byte errors, which is a topic in computer architecture (cs.AR).
